      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a solid daily driver. The exterior shows its age with some clear coat peeling on the hood and roof, along with various scratches and a minor dent on the rear passenger door. Inside, the upholstery has some visible staining and the driver's seat shows significant bolster wear, but all essential electronics and climate controls are fully functional. Mechanically, it has been regularly serviced, though it does have a small oil leak that will need monitoring. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it is a hardworking, honest car that still has plenty of life left.",
