      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is seriously in showroom condition\u2014not a single scratch or dent to be found! It drives like it just rolled off the lot, and the interior still feels brand new. I've taken such good care of it, and I'm honestly a bit sad to see it go, but it's time for someone else to enjoy this flawless ride. You won't find another one this clean! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
