    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents a superlative example of the high-revving S65B40 naturally aspirated V8 era. Meticulously maintained, the engine features documented preventative rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring mechanical longevity. The 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp gates, paired with a factory M-Variable differential for optimal power delivery. The chassis is structurally pristine, exhibiting zero subframe fatigue or oxidation. Finished in original paint with no discernible swirl marks, and an interior featuring supple, matte-finish Novillo leather, this vehicle delivers a visceral 8,400 RPM redline experience in a showroom-preserved state.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
